@endgroup

@group sendDocument
@endpoint POST /sendDocument
@desc Use this method to send general files. On success, the sent [Message](https://core.telegram.org/bots/api/#message) is returned. Bots can currently send files of any type of up to 50 MB in size, this limit may be changed in the future.
