@endgroup

@group sendVideo
@endpoint POST /sendVideo
@desc Use this method to send video files, Telegram clients support mp4 videos (other formats may be sent as [Document](https://core.telegram.org/bots/api/#document)). On success, the sent [Message](https://core.telegram.org/bots/api/#message) is returned. Bots can currently send video files of up to 50 MB in size, this limit may be changed in the future.
