@endgroup

@group sendAnimation
@endpoint POST /sendAnimation
@desc Use this method to send animation files (GIF or H.264/MPEG-4 AVC video without sound). On success, the sent [Message](https://core.telegram.org/bots/api/#message) is returned. Bots can currently send animation files of up to 50 MB in size, this limit may be changed in the future.
